	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_FORTIFIED_BORDERS_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Balance of Power</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_FORTIFIED_BORDERS_HELP">
			<Text>Times are changing. Those who ally themselves to Autocracy will triumph. Those who turn away from our creed will perish in the flames of war! We must save all we can.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_FORTIFIED_BORDERS_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Libraries yield -2 [ICON_RESEARCH] Science but +2 [ICON_GOLDEN_AGE] Golden Age Points.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_FORTIFIED_BORDERS_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Police Stations consume -4 [ICON_GOLD] Gold but generate +4 [ICON_GOLDEN_AGE] Golden Age Points.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_FORTIFIED_BORDERS_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>The Foreign Office generates +5 [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_FORTIFIED_BORDERS_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>History is a lie, written by the victors: sympathisers of Freedom and Order. We must destroy the lies of the past, and free our young people from those shackles.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_FORTIFIED_BORDERS_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Not everyone will be strong enough to accept our destiny. Make sure our secret police are well funded. When the time comes, these naysayers will need to be gotten rid of.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_FORTIFIED_BORDERS_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>The dreary Empires that have set themselves in our path are filled with disconteted men and women, who yearn for the victory Autocracy shall bring. We must extend a hand of friendship to them, so that they might know they are welcome in our glorious nation.</Text>
		</Row>
